# Monitor Design System

Replicate Monitor's visual design in this app. Use Tailwind utilities with `cn()` / CVA. Define theme tokens in `src/styles.css` (`@theme`, CSS variables) — don't scatter one-off hex values in components.

**Dark mode**: class-based — `.dark` on `<html>`. Variant: `@custom-variant dark (&:where(.dark, .dark *));`

**Default border override**: `border-color: var(--color-monitor-gray-200)` (`#202020`) instead of `currentcolor`.

---

## 1. Design Tokens

### Colors — Brand / Accent

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `monitor` | `#6b16ed` | Primary accent (light) |
| `monitor-50` | `#f5f0ff` | Highlighted button bg (light) |
| `monitor-100` | `#7317ff` | Highlighted button hover (dark), scrollbar thumb |
| `monitor-200` | `#5a12c7` | Highlighted button text (light) |
| `monitor-300` | `#4a0fa3` | Deepest brand shade |
| `warning` / `warning-400` | `#fcd452` | Primary accent (dark mode) |

### Warning Scale (dark accent + callouts)

`warning-50` `#fefce8` · `warning-100` `#fef9c3` · `warning-200` `#fef08a` · `warning-300` `#fde047` · `warning-400` `#fcd452` · `warning-500` `#facc15` · `warning-600` `#ca8a04` · `warning-700` `#a16207` · `warning-800` `#854d0e` · `warning-900` `#713f12`

### Neutral Grays (dark backgrounds)

| Token | Hex | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `base` | `#101010` | Page background (dark) |
| `monitor-gray-100` | `#181818` | Component background (dark) |
| `monitor-gray-200` | `#202020` | Elevated surface / borders (dark) |
| `monitor-gray-300` | `#242424` | Input border shadow / hover (dark) |
| `monitor-gray-400` | `#282828` | Tooltip background (dark) |
| `monitor-gray-500` | `#323232` | Subtle hover overlays (dark) |

### Semantic

| Token | Hex |
|---|---|
| `success` | `#22C55E` |
| `error` | `#dc2626` |

### Light Mode Defaults

Page `gray-50` · components `white` · borders `neutral-200` · text `black` · muted `neutral-500` · placeholder `neutral-300`

### Accent Swap

| Context | Light | Dark |
|---|---|---|
| Primary accent | `monitor` | `warning` |
| Focus ring | `ring-monitor` | `ring-warning` |
| Input focus bar | `#6b16ed` | `#fcd452` |
| Active nav | `text-black` | `text-warning` |
| Helper/highlight | `text-monitor` | `text-warning` |
| Spinner | `text-monitor` | `text-warning` |

### Background Hierarchy

**Dark**: `base` → `monitor-gray-100` → `monitor-gray-200` → `monitor-gray-300` → `monitor-gray-400` → `monitor-gray-500`

**Light**: `gray-50` → `white` → `neutral-200` → `neutral-100` → `neutral-300`

