## 2. Typography

Font: **Inter**, sans-serif (`font-display: swap`). Body: `text-sm antialiased`.

**CRITICAL — dark mode headings**: h1–h4, card titles, modal titles MUST be `dark:text-white`. Default body in dark is `neutral-400` (`#a3a3a3`); headings without override are nearly invisible.

| Element | Classes |
|---|---|
| h1 | `text-3xl font-bold dark:text-white` |
| h2 | `text-xl font-bold dark:text-white` |
| h3 | `text-lg font-bold dark:text-white` |
| h4 | `text-base font-bold dark:text-white` |
| Labels | `text-sm font-medium` |
| Badge/status | `text-xs font-bold` |
| Box description | `text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500` |

