## 4. Focus & Input Shadows

**Buttons, links, checkboxes** — ring system (not inputs):

```
focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-monitor
dark:focus-visible:ring-warning focus-visible:ring-offset-2 dark:focus-visible:ring-offset-base
```

**Inputs & selects** — inset box-shadow (not ring). Enables dirty-state left bar:

```
/* default light */  inset 4px 0 0 transparent, inset 0 0 0 2px #e5e5e5
/* default dark */   inset 4px 0 0 transparent, inset 0 0 0 2px #242424
/* focus/dirty light */ inset 4px 0 0 #6b16ed, inset 0 0 0 2px #e5e5e5
/* focus/dirty dark */  inset 4px 0 0 #fcd452, inset 0 0 0 2px #242424
/* disabled/readonly */ none
```

Input-sticky variant uses 1px inset border instead of 2px. **Textareas** use a normal border + ring focus — NOT the inset left-bar system.

