## 5. Components

Use CVA variants (`default`, `highlighted`, `error`) — not string flags with switch chains.

### Button — Default

```
flex gap-2 justify-center items-center px-2 h-8 text-sm text-black normal-case rounded-sm
border-2 outline-0 cursor-pointer font-medium bg-white border-neutral-200 hover:bg-neutral-100
dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:text-white dark:hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-monitor-gray-200
dark:border-monitor-gray-300 disabled:cursor-not-allowed min-w-fit
dark:disabled:text-neutral-600 disabled:border-transparent disabled:hover:bg-transparent
disabled:bg-transparent disabled:text-neutral-300
+ focus ring classes above
```

### Button — Highlighted (`variant: highlighted`)

```
text-monitor-200 dark:text-white bg-monitor-50 dark:bg-monitor/20
border-monitor dark:border-monitor-100 hover:bg-monitor hover:text-white
dark:hover:bg-monitor-100 dark:hover:text-white
```

### Button — Error (`variant: error`)

```
text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/30
border-red-300 dark:border-red-800 hover:bg-red-300 hover:text-white
dark:hover:bg-red-800 dark:hover:text-white
```

Loading: spinner SVG `animate-spin` beside content — `text-monitor dark:text-warning`.

### Input / Select

```
block py-1.5 w-full text-sm text-black rounded-sm border-0
dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:text-white
disabled:bg-neutral-200 disabled:text-neutral-500 dark:disabled:bg-monitor-gray-100/40
placeholder:text-neutral-300 dark:placeholder:text-neutral-700
read-only:text-neutral-500 read-only:bg-neutral-200
dark:read-only:text-neutral-500 dark:read-only:bg-monitor-gray-100/40
focus-visible:outline-none
```

Select: add chevron SVG via `background-image`, `appearance-none`, `pr-10`. Dark arrow stroke `#ffffff`.

Password inputs: `pr-10` (or `pr-[2.4rem]`).

### Textarea

```
block w-full text-sm font-mono rounded-sm border border-neutral-200
dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:text-white dark:border-monitor-gray-300
focus-visible:outline-none + ring classes (not inset shadow)
```

### Checkbox

```
dark:border-neutral-700 text-monitor-gray-400 dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 rounded-sm
dark:disabled:bg-base dark:disabled:cursor-not-allowed + focus ring
```

Container: `flex flex-row items-center gap-4 pr-2 py-1 min-w-fit dark:hover:bg-monitor-gray-100 cursor-pointer`

### Box / Card — Standard

```
relative flex lg:flex-row flex-col p-2 transition-colors cursor-pointer min-h-[4rem]
dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 shadow-sm bg-white border text-black dark:text-white
border-neutral-200 dark:border-monitor-gray-300 hover:bg-neutral-100
dark:hover:bg-monitor-100 dark:hover:text-white rounded-sm
```

**On hover, child text must flip** — description (`neutral-500`) is invisible on purple hover:

```
hover:[&_.box-title]:text-black hover:[&_.box-description]:text-black
dark:hover:[&_.box-title]:text-white dark:hover:[&_.box-description]:text-white
```

Box title: `font-bold text-black dark:text-white` (never grey in dark). Description: `text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500`.

### Monitor-Box (ring hover)

```
relative flex p-2 rounded min-h-[4rem] transition-all duration-150
bg-white dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 border border-neutral-200 dark:border-monitor-gray-400
hover:ring-2 hover:ring-monitor dark:hover:ring-warning cursor-pointer
```

### Badge / Status

Dot: `inline-block w-3 h-3 rounded-full border border-neutral-200 dark:border-black`

| Status | Dot | Text |
|---|---|---|
| Running | `bg-success` | `text-success` |
| Stopped | `bg-error` | `text-error` |
| Degraded / Restarting | `bg-warning` | `dark:text-warning` |

### Dropdown

Container: `p-1 mt-1 bg-white border rounded-sm shadow-sm dark:bg-monitor-gray-200 dark:border-monitor-gray-300 border-neutral-300`

Item: `flex gap-2 items-center py-1 pr-4 pl-2 w-full text-xs cursor-pointer dark:text-white hover:bg-neutral-100 dark:hover:bg-monitor focus-visible:bg-neutral-100 dark:focus-visible:bg-monitor`

### Sidebar / Navigation

- Fixed left sidebar desktop: `lg:fixed lg:inset-y-0 lg:z-50 lg:w-56 lg:flex-col`
- Main offset: `lg:pl-56`
- Main padding: `p-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-6`
- Nav: `flex flex-col flex-1 px-2 bg-white border-r dark:bg-base dark:border-monitor-gray-200 border-neutral-300`
- Mobile topbar: `sticky top-0 z-40 lg:hidden bg-white/95 dark:bg-base/95 backdrop-blur-sm border-b`
- Hamburger icon: `dark:text-warning`

Menu item: `flex gap-3 items-center px-2 py-1 w-full text-sm rounded-sm truncate dark:hover:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:hover:text-white hover:bg-neutral-300`

Active: `text-black bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-monitor-gray-200 dark:text-warning`

Logo: `text-2xl font-bold tracking-wide dark:text-white`

### Callout

Base: `relative p-4 border rounded-lg`. Types: `warning`, `danger`, `info`, `success`.

| Type | BG | Border | Title | Body |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| warning | `bg-warning-50 dark:bg-warning-900/30` | `border-warning-300 dark:border-warning-800` | `text-warning-800 dark:text-warning-300` | `text-warning-700 dark:text-warning-200` |
| danger | `bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-900/30` | `border-red-300 dark:border-red-800` | `text-red-800 dark:text-red-300` | `text-red-700 dark:text-red-200` |
| info | `bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/30` | `border-blue-300 dark:border-blue-800` | `text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300` | `text-blue-700 dark:text-blue-200` |
| success | `bg-green-50 dark:bg-green-900/30` | `border-green-300 dark:border-green-800` | `text-green-800 dark:text-green-300` | `text-green-700 dark:text-green-200` |

### Toast

`shadow-[0_5px_15px_-3px_rgb(0_0_0_/_0.08)] bg-white dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:border dark:border-monitor-gray-200 rounded-sm sm:max-w-xs`

Stack max 4, auto-dismiss 4s, bottom-right. Icon colors: success `text-green-500`, info `text-blue-500`, warning `text-orange-400`, danger `text-red-500`.

### Modal

`rounded-sm max-h-[calc(100vh-5rem)] flex flex-col`. Input variant: `bg-white dark:bg-base border-neutral-200 dark:border-monitor-gray-300`. Confirmation: `bg-neutral-100 dark:bg-base min-w-full lg:min-w-[36rem] max-w-[48rem]`. Header title: `text-lg font-bold dark:text-white`.

### Slide-Over

`fixed inset-y-0 right-0 pl-10` · panel `max-w-xl w-screen h-full py-6 border-l shadow-lg bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-base dark:border-neutral-800`

### Tag

`px-2 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-neutral-500 bg-neutral-100 hover:bg-neutral-200 dark:bg-monitor-gray-100 dark:hover:bg-monitor-gray-300 cursor-pointer`

### Spinner

`w-4 h-4 text-monitor dark:text-warning animate-spin`

### Helper / Tooltip

Trigger: `cursor-pointer text-monitor dark:text-warning`

Popup: `absolute z-40 text-xs rounded-sm max-w-sm p-4 bg-neutral-200 text-neutral-700 dark:bg-monitor-gray-400 dark:text-neutral-300 dark:border dark:border-monitor-gray-500`

### Highlighted Text

`inline-block font-bold text-monitor dark:text-warning`

### Kbd

`px-2 text-xs rounded-sm border border-dashed border-neutral-700 dark:text-warning`

### Table

`min-w-full border-collapse separate`. Dark rows: `text-neutral-400`, hover `bg-black`. Light hover `bg-neutral-200`. `th` uppercase, `dark:text-white`. First `td`/`th`: extra left padding, first `td` bold.

### Scrollbar

`scrollbar-thin scrollbar-thumb-monitor-100 scrollbar-track-neutral-200 dark:scrollbar-track-monitor-gray-200`

